import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

const layoutProps = {
  
};
export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"real-estate-events-api"}}>{`Real Estate Events API`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="p">{`version 0.0.1`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`A specification for describing real estate data and events in common way`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"servers"}}>{`Servers`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="table" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="thead" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="thead">
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":"left"}}>{`Stage`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":"left"}}>{`Entrypoint`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tbody" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":"left"}}>{`demo`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":"left"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="td" props={{"href":"https://real-estate.yodata.me/"}}>{`https://real-estate.yodata.me/`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"security"}}>{`Security`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`SoftPro events will be authenticated by API Key in the http request header.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`API Key is not yet requred in development.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-shell"}}>{`GET / HTTP/1.1
Accept: */*
x-api-key: xxxxx
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
